high_descs: Turn right, move to the counter in front of the dishwasher.
Pick up the knife from the counter.

Section the apple in the sink.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn left, move to in front of the sink.
Pick up a section of apple from the sink.

Put the apple section in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.

high_descs: Turn right then head to the counter beside the microwave
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left then head to the sink
Slice the apple in the sink
Turn right then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the knife then close the fridge
Turn left head to the sink
Pick up a slice of apple
Turn right and head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the slice apple
Turn right walk forward to the trash bin
Put the slice apple in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter with a microwave on top.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter between the metal bowl and the gray knife.
Turn left and go to the front of the sink.
Cut the apple inside the sink into three parts.
Turn around to go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife inside the refrigerator on the left of the mug.
Turn left to go back to the sink.
Take out one piece of apple from the sink.
Turn around and go back to the front of the refrigerator.
Remove the apple after cooling it on the top shelf in the refrigerator.
Turn around to go to the green trash can on the floor on the left of the stove.
Place the apple inside the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a chilled piece of apple.
